title: Arista Switches DCS-7280: Temperature
agents: snmp
catalog: hw/network/arista
license: GPLv2
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check monitors the temperature sensors of an Arista Networks devices.

 You can manually configure upper and lower temperature levels.

 There are no default temperature levels in the check plugin nor does the
 device provides their own thershold levels.

 The service goes {WARN}/{CRIT} if temperature exceeds these levels.

 This check uses the ENTITY-MIB.

item:
 One service is created for each recognized temperature sensor

discovery:
 All temperature known sensors with complete Physical description are detected
